Nighty Night for the second time... :)

Okay so today was um....fun. Mz. Kaity Crandall slept over mi casa last night at the late time of 9:45 because I didn't get service in Mr. Rienzo's house so therefore whenever somebody called me my phone never rang! So that was pretty nuts. Then me being an idiot that I am was outside in the rain last night..now I feel like crap-ola. Kaity left in the wee-hours of the morning (7) for her fencing tourney. I felt bad...she was so tired and I felt like I was commiting a crime when I woke her up lol. So after I groggily walked her to the door I ran back upstairs and slept for about another 4 hours. So after waking up at around 10:40ish I decided to drag my lazy bum to the mall to try to find new jeans...It's kind of ironic I bought holey jeans from AE in the beginning of the school yeah and the once small hole is now the size of my knee! So as I forced myself through the mall while feeling like crap I found an AWESOME scarf that I seriously just fell head over heels in love with. That made my day :). After that I had to go to best buy for mi padre to buy ink cartrages? wtf...who sends a 16 year old female for computer accesories? Nuts...Im telling you. But while I was there I caught a glimpse of the Seether cd..so I bought it and have been jamming to it since. Soooo after that Kim called me and was all frantic and sounded like she was going to die so I was like "okay kim, if I bring you food, will you feel better?" and of course she agreed...So I drove to Wendy's and then went to Kim's for a while. So on my attempt to leave..Kim walks me out to my car and then the most scariest thing was in my subaru..a BEE! I stood around for 5 minutes waiting for that thing to fly out of my car with the fear I was going to be stung. Finally, It left and I had a great wave of relief. I drove home and then just collapsed on my bed....feeling like crap and really really just sick. After telling Jarrod for about an hour that I felt like such a jerk for not being able to hang out with steve and others tonight He finally just coaxed me out of feeling bad and to "get rest" so that is what I did....I napped :)! It was great, Napping is such a wonderful thing. But a long with feeling crappy other things have been going through my mind...which will stay there since I don't want to put TOO much information on this live journal. But anywhom this is my first journal and It's going to end here since I have got to chiz-at with KAYTE My love! :) So Gute Nacht all!
